# Data Structure
## TotalV3Item (object)
+ name (string, required) icons style name
+ `api_code` (enum[string], required) - icons style code; in other places it named `plarform` or `platform_api_code`
    + Members
        + `all`
        + `ios7`
        + `win8`
        + `win10`
        + `android`
        + `androidL`
        + `color`
        + `office`
+ total (number, required) the quantity of icons
